[BID X] This is a perfect takeout double: 17 HCP, a singleton in opener's suit, and 4-4-4 in the three unbid suits. You're at the top of the range, so plan to bid again over a minimum response.
[BID 3H] Partner responded 2\H. With 17 HCP and four-card heart support you're way too good to pass — raise to 3\H, an invitational raise asking partner to bid game with anything extra.
